com.silabs.bluetooth_mesh

Class GroupInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.silabs.bluetooth_mesh.GroupInfo

  • public class GroupInfo
extends java.lang.Object
    Class that represents a Group in the Mesh Network, it is responsible to provide all the variables according to the Bluetooth Mesh Specification

      • GroupInfo

        public GroupInfo(java.lang.String name,
                 NetworkInfo net,
                 int appkeyIndex,
                 byte[] appKey,
                 int pubAddress,
                 int subAddress)
        Class constructor, responsible to set the minimal necessary variables for a Group
        Parameters:
        name - String containing the group name
        net - NetworkInfo object that this group is going to be attached to
        appkeyIndex - Integer containing the desired appkeyIndex
        appKey - byte[16] containing the application key (Normally Random)
        pubAddress - Integer containing the publish address of this group
        subAddress - Integet containing the subscribe address of this group
